## Required properties of validator devices

Persistent DID and public key stored in secure element/TPM.

Provisioned attestation certificate chain (optionally from a manufacturer or platform CA).

GNSS (or other location mechanism) and time sync (NTP/PTP + signed monotonic counter).

Minimum sensor set available for telemetry cross-checks (e.g., accelerometer, IMU, magnetometer, camera, ambient metrics).

Network connectivity to fetch job spec + artifacts and to send attestation.

A light-weight deterministic simulator/validator runtime (container) capable of verifying checkpoints or running N steps.



